OL,3,CTeachers to take industrial action
OL,4,Cafter rejecting pay offer
OL,6,FThe majority of teachers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland are set to start industrial
OL,8,Faction short of striking after
OL,9,Frejecting a pay offer.
OL,11,FA 5.5% pay offer for 2024/25 was
OL,12,Foffered by the employers last week.
OL,14,FThe Northern Ireland Teachers' Council
OL,15,F(NITC), made up of the five main
OL,16,Fteaching unions, said that after
OL,17,Fconsultation with members they were
OL,18,Fnot in a position to ratify the
OL,19,Fagreement on the offer.
