OL,3,CTeachers to take industrial action
OL,4,Cafter rejecting pay offer
OL,6,FThey said all constituent members of
OL,7,FNITC remain committed to engaging in
OL,8,Ffurther negotiations in an effort to
OL,9,Freach a clear and unrestricted pay
OL,10,Faward.
OL,12,FNITC chair Jacquie White, who is
OL,13,Fgeneral secretary of the Ulster
OL,14,FTeachers' Union (UTU), said UTU
OL,15,Fmembers had raised concerns around the
OL,16,Fclarity of the offer and indicated
OL,17,Fthat they were unable to accept at
OL,18,Fthis time.
