OL,3,CTeachers to take industrial action
OL,4,Cafter rejecting pay offer
OL,6,F"We do, however, remain committed to
OL,7,Fseeking a way forward which delivers
OL,8,Fresolution for our members," she said.
OL,10,FNITC secretary Mark McTaggart, who is
OL,11,Falso Irish National Teacher
OL,12,FOrganisation (INTO) northern
OL,13,Fsecretary, said their members had said
OL,14,Fthey were unhappy with the perceived
OL,15,Frestrictions included in last week's
OL,16,Foffer.
OL,18,F"It is disappointing that ongoing
OL,19,Fnegotiations have failed to find an
OL,20,Famicable resolution," he said.
