OL,3,CTeachers to take industrial action
OL,4,Cafter rejecting pay offer
OL,6,FMeanwhile, members of the National
OL,7,FAssociation of Head Teachers (NAHT NI)
OL,8,Fhave voted to accept the pay offer.
OL,10,FNAHT NI national secretary Graham
OL,11,FGault said: "While the membership of
OL,12,FNAHT voted in favour of accepting the
OL,13,Foffer, the wider NITC position means
OL,14,Fthat the offer has not been ratified
OL,15,Fby all unions and will, therefore, not
OL,16,Fbe progressed in its current form.
