OL,3,CTeachers to take industrial action
OL,4,Cafter rejecting pay offer
OL,6,F"The NAHT will, therefore, engage
OL,7,Ffully with our own membership to
OL,8,Fconsider our next steps while also
OL,9,Fremaining committed to working
OL,10,Fcollectively with others to secure an
OL,11,Foffer that can be accepted by all
OL,12,Fparties."
OL,14,FResponding, the management side of the
OL,15,FTeachers' Negotiating Committee
OL,16,Fexpressed disappointment.
OL,18,FThey described a "substantial offer of
OL,19,F5.5% as well as wide-ranging
OL,20,Fcommitments on workload issues".
